<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>ArduinoWeb</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", media: "all", "data-turbolinks-track" => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application", "data-turbolinks-track" => true %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
  
<body>
<%=flash[:notice] if flash[:notice] %>
<%=flash[:alert] if flash[:alert] %>
 
<div class="navbar navbar-fixed-top">
    <div class="navbar-inner">
      <div class="container">
        <%= link_to "Arduino", root_path, :class => "brand" %>
         <div class='session-controls'>
            <% if current_user %>
              <%= link_to "Log Out", logout_path, :class => 'btn btn-primary btn-mini' %>
              Logged in as <%= current_user.email %>.
            <% else %>
              <div class="btn-group">
                <%= link_to "Sign Up", signup_path, :class => "btn btn-mini" %>
                <%= link_to "Log In", login_path, :class => "btn btn-mini" %>
              </div>
            <% end %>
         </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="span4">
      <% flash.each do |name, msg| %>
        <%= content_tag :div, msg, id: "flash_#{name}" %>
      <% end %>
      </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="span9">
        <%= yield %>
      </div>
      <div class="span3 sidebar">
        <div class="my-arduino-site">
          <h4>My Arduino</h4>
          <ul>
            <li><%= link_to "Name", root_path %></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="categories-sidebar">
          <h4>Gadget Functions</h4> 
          <ul>
            <li><%= link_to "Control a gadget", root_path %></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="about">
          <h4>About Arduino</h4>
             <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Accusantium architecto earum neque perspiciatis quia animi debitis quod repellat vitae explicabo. Sapiente aliquam reprehenderit id vitae atque ducimus facere molestias soluta?</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
